Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.board

Class Cell

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.board.Cell
public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a cell on the board. A cell may contain a worker and always contains a Tower object.

    • getHeightDifference

      public int getHeightDifference​(Cell other)
      Computes the height difference between two towers. The difference is taken by calculating the height of other minus the height of this. The towers must not be complete (i.e. They must not have a Dome on top)
      Parameters:
      other - the other Cell with which to compute the difference
      Returns:
      an int representing the height difference.
